    "text": [
        "Dear Sir or Madam,",
        "Hope my letter finds you well.",
        "I am writing this letter to inform you that I would like to book a birthday party in your restaurant.",
        "Please be informed that this coming Saturday is my mother's 50th birthday, thus, I would like to give her a surprise party. Furthermore, I would like to ask if you could arrange a band that can be performed during the party.",
        "I appreciated it if you could let me know the price for that night and the inclusion of that price. Also, I would like to ask if you could share with me in advance the list of food for the party and if you have a promotion that I can avail of. Please do let me know what I need to do to secure the booking and the availability of the venue.",
        "Should you have any concerns regarding my letter, please do not hesitate to contact me on my mobile number. Looking forward to hearing from you soon.",
        "Yours faithfully,",
        "Alwen Ampatin"
